Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,誰管你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.38,0:23:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.18,0:23:27.68,Top,,0,0,0,,用了這個就能改變自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,還要約會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:29.67,Top,,0,0,0,,變得大膽起來
